@Gregsly
Hi and, I assume, welcome. If this is your first incursion into this group, take heart. Thursdays are always extra crunchy, with puzzles within puzzles.  So, yes, rules are broken on Thursdays. And sometimes other days have their own little treats. But most days of the week will have something like a standard crossword, with difficulty levels increasing Mon-Sat,  and Sundays being extra large but not extra tough. 
Of late, this weekly pattern seems to have come under stress and deviations have been noted. But it's still good puzzling here most days and the Commentariat is remarkable.

